a:50:{i:1132953;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1132953";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Bliss";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"255";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Ark_Angel";s:4:"text";s:481:"Bliss&#039; smile turns into a smirk. God that bird can be so frakking cute sometimes...[br]Bliss kisses Ark&#039;s beak again, this time a little more firmly. &quot;Number one. Be honest, be open. If you do somethin&#039; with someone, tell me. As soon as you can. If you&#039;re planning somethin&#039; in advance, tell me. Before it happens. If I find out through someone else, it&#039;ll be really sad... And all that, all that there? I&#039;ll do the same for you. Cool?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417690777";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f11ea7";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14176907868";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#30d5d7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1132962;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1132962";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:4:"7081";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Ark_Angel";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"703";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Bliss";s:4:"text";s:365:"/me nodded, smiling. &ldquo;Cool,&rdquo; she said. And with that, Ark turned her head away and glanced at the comfort of the pillows. Without restraint, she fell into them, for the most part on her face. &ldquo;You still vant to talk about my mum?&rdquo; she mumbled into the pillows. The one eye of hers not face-down in the covers looked up at Bliss as she asked.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417691032";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffdb00";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14176909622";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffee88";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1132964;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1132964";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Bliss";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"255";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Ark_Angel";s:4:"text";s:278:"/me lets Ark lay down, although really she was quite enjoying the closeness.[br]&quot;Heh, yeah. In a sec. There&#039;s still 3 more &#039;rules&#039; I should cover, if you&#039;re okay with &#039;em. Again, I wanna avoid surprises. Last thing I wanna do is get you hurt.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417691299";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f11ea7";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14176913086";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#30d5d7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1132968;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1132968";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:4:"7081";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Ark_Angel";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"703";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Bliss";s:4:"text";s:228:"/me&rsquo;s one eye lowered its brow a little. &ldquo;Oh,&rdquo; she said, starting to roll onto her back now. &ldquo;Keep going, zen.&rdquo; [br]Ark laughed it off, but she was clearly embarrassed about jumping the gun on that.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417691406";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffdb00";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14176913349";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffee88";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1132976;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1132976";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Bliss";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"255";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Ark_Angel";s:4:"text";s:398:"Bliss lays down onto her own side, still looking pretty happy, her eyes idly wandering over Ark&#039;s features in the meantime.[br]&quot;Second, then... hard drugs, major life change stuff, family issues. All that kind of stuff. Same deal as rule 1. Tell me before I find out, you know? It&#039;s less important, kinda, but I wanna be able to help. It&#039;s more a helpin&#039; thing, yeah?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417692366";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f11ea7";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14176923754";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#30d5d7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1132977;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1132977";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:4:"7081";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Ark_Angel";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"703";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Bliss";s:4:"text";s:137:"/me chuckled. &ldquo;It goes vizout saying -- no [i]hard[/i] drugs,&rdquo; she said, giving Bliss a wink. [br]&ldquo;Anyzing else?&rdquo;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417692485";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffdb00";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14176924719";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffee88";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1132980;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1132980";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Bliss";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"255";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Ark_Angel";s:4:"text";s:491:"&quot;well, yeah. Getting addicted to somethin&#039; that&#039;s only gonna hurt you just ain&#039;t worth it.&quot; She says, both from experience and common sense. She can appreciate the humor though.[br]&quot;Third is kinda like point one, but for other people. If you&#039;re gonna get physical with someone, tell &#039;em that you&#039;re with me, and that I&#039;m cool with that. Don&#039;t lead anyone on into a situation they don&#039;t like, right? It saves a lot of trouble.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417692754";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f11ea7";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14176927632";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#30d5d7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1132981;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1132981";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:4:"7081";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Ark_Angel";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"703";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Bliss";s:4:"text";s:310:"/me paused, thinking for a moment. &ldquo;You did not just make up zese rules,&rdquo; she replied eventually. &ldquo;You&rsquo;ve done zis type of arrangement before, haven&rsquo;t you?&rdquo; And considering she was doing it again, Ark had reason to believe that the times before this hadn&rsquo;t worked out.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417692906";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffdb00";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14176928932";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffee88";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1132982;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1132982";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Bliss";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"255";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Ark_Angel";s:4:"text";s:448:"/me winces a little. Admittedly, no, but not for the reason that she might be thinking.[br]&quot;The system works because I&#039;m broken. I... work less, and the world works less.&quot; She reasons. &quot;If you really want to know, dude? The first person died, the second got too busy and I got too depressed to keep going as a &#039;relationship&#039; and the third is you.&quot; She frowns, really wishing she didn&#039;t have to get into this.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417693150";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f11ea7";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14176931597";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#30d5d7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1132983;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1132983";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:4:"7081";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Ark_Angel";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"703";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Bliss";s:4:"text";s:295:"/me looked taken back, and perhaps a bit regretful about asking the question. &ldquo;Sorry,&rdquo; Ark said, seeming to notice she&rsquo;d struck a bit of a nerve. &ldquo;I agree to ze rules. No vorries from me.&rdquo; The griffin smiled warmly at her friend. &ldquo;Now, my mozer&hellip;&rdquo;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417693388";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffdb00";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14176933754";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffee88";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1132990;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1132990";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Bliss";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"255";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Ark_Angel";s:4:"text";s:102:"/me smirks a little, a short huff of amusement escaping her. &quot;Last point, love. Point four.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417695208";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f11ea7";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14176952178";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#30d5d7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1132991;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1132991";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:4:"7081";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Ark_Angel";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"703";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Bliss";s:4:"text";s:50:"/me put her face back in the pillows with a groan.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417695273";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffdb00";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14176952476";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffee88";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1132992;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1132992";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Bliss";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"255";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Ark_Angel";s:4:"text";s:133:"/me rolls closer to Ark and flops 1/3 on 2/3 off of her in a lazy hug, giggling softly. &quot;We&#039;ll get there~. I promise.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417695331";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f11ea7";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14176953404";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#30d5d7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1132993;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1132993";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:4:"7081";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Ark_Angel";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"703";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Bliss";s:4:"text";s:131:"/me rested her head on its side, her golden eyes making contact with Bliss&rsquo;. Ready to listen, she waited for the fourth rule.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417695405";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffdb00";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14176953798";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffee88";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1132994;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1132